{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"78fbb24de7","title":"周恩来对贺龙专案组请示报告的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"91a6747fee","index":0,"year":1970,"month":12,"day":3,"articleId":"78fbb24de7","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"汪东兴","id":"3c11982f62","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"邓小平","id":"5bd9678625","type":"人物"},{"name":"叶群","id":"62ff3f0cef","type":"人物"},{"name":"谭震林","id":"89f0012853","type":"人物"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"各级党政领导人","id":"a59dfa2519","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"贺龙","id":"d0a2337495","type":"人物"},{"name":"吴法宪","id":"fa1994871e","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f15b31f1df","type":"title","text":"周恩来对贺龙专案组请示报告的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2d830e9c9f","type":"paragraph","text":"“东兴同志，这全部是公开文件，请你考虑是否需全部调阅。我记得在下放邓小平、谭震林时，已将两人从专案组撤消。现专案组既又重新提出查此人，可否先告专案组将邓小平以三反罪行、招降纳叛线索写一报告来，以便拟此查阅。周恩来。”","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cab0cc3d42","type":"paragraph","text":"附一","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"723521fcaa","type":"paragraph","text":"贺龙专案组的报告","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"74b73c8fcd","type":"paragraph","text":"康生、永胜、法宪、叶群同志：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a12ab3f1c","type":"paragraph","text":"关于邓小平的三反罪行，招降纳叛等问题，经过调查，我们已掌握了不少材料和线索，但其中有些问题的核实和查证，还需要查阅一些档案材料。为此，我们拟到中央档案馆、中办机要室等单位查阅有关材料，并对必要的部分拍照取证。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3390b35b2c","type":"paragraph","text":"是否妥当，请批示。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ec4b5f89d8","type":"paragraph","text":"附：申请查档目录表。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"75f1820a89","type":"paragraph","text":"贺龙专案组","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f25f9caf36","type":"paragraph","text":"1970年11月28日","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"171c1b12b6","type":"paragraph","text":"附二：","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"957d651feb","type":"paragraph","text":"吴法宪对贺龙专案组报告的批示：","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a35f348192","type":"paragraph","text":"可否查这些档案，呈请总理、汪东兴同志批示。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"905f19fde2","type":"paragraph","text":"1970.11.30","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"78fbb24de7","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}